OL,3,CNew owner of Gloucestershire Airport
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FThe new owner of Gloucestershire
OL,7,FAirport has been revealed as Horizon
OL,8,FAero Group.
OL,10,FThe company is a joint venture between
OL,11,FVayu Aviation Services Ltd (UK) and
OL,12,FVensa Infrastructure Ltd (India).
OL,14,FHorizon says its key aims are to drive
OL,15,Fjob creation, upskilling the local
OL,16,Fworkforce and enhancing the airport's
OL,17,Frole as a community and economic asset.
OL,19,FRamdev Polkampalli, chairman, Horizon
OL,20,FAero Group Ltd, said: "We are honoured
OL,21,Fto be selected as the preferred bidder.
