OL,6,F"Gloucestershire Airport holds
OL,7,Fenormous promise, and we are committed
OL,8,Fto preserving its heritage while
OL,9,Finvesting in its future.
OL,11,F"We look forward to working
OL,12,Fcollaboratively with both councils,
OL,13,Fairport staff, and local stakeholders
OL,14,Fto ensure a smooth and transparent
OL,15,Fjourney toward completion."
OL,17,FThe 375-acre Staverton airport was
OL,18,Fjointly owned by Cheltenham Borough
OL,19,Fand Gloucester City Council.
