OL,3,CNew owner of Gloucestershire Airport
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FThe site was run by Gloucestershire
OL,7,FAirport Limited which was established
OL,8,Fin 1993 - both councils had a 50 per
OL,9,Fcent shareholding.
OL,11,FHowever, the two authorities revealed
OL,12,Fin November 2023 their intention to
OL,13,Fdispose of the site which has
OL,14,Fstruggled commercially and needed a
OL,15,Flarge investment expand its business
OL,16,Fparks.
OL,18,FThe councillors gave the go-ahead to
OL,19,Fsell the airport to new buyers at a
OL,20,Ffull council meeting on 26 June.
