OL,6,FCouncillor Rowena Hay, leader of
OL,7,FCheltenham Borough Council, said: "The
OL,8,Fairport is a strategic asset for
OL,9,FGloucestershire.
OL,11,F"We're encouraged by Horizon's
OL,12,Fcommunity-first and sustainability-
OL,13,Ffocused approach.
OL,15,F"We want to reassure the public that
OL,16,Fany final deal will uphold the long-
OL,17,Fterm aviation future of the airport
OL,18,Fand deliver clear benefits to the
OL,19,Fwider region."
