OL,6,FLeader of Gloucester City Council,
OL,7,FCouncillor Jeremy Hilton, said: "We
OL,8,Fwere impressed by Horizon's enthusiasm
OL,9,Ffor the airport and their clear
OL,10,Frecognition of its potential to play
OL,11,Fan important role in the economic
OL,12,Fgrowth of the region.
OL,14,F"They share our vision of
OL,15,Fmodernisation and building on it as a
OL,16,Fplace to do business, in turn bringing
OL,17,Fhuge benefits to the area."
