OL,6,FJason Ivey, managing director of
OL,7,FGloucestershire Airport, said: "I have
OL,8,Fbeen really impressed with my
OL,9,Finteractions with the Horizon Aero
OL,10,FGroup during the sale process, as this
OL,11,Fis clearly a company that has the
OL,12,Fenergy and a focussed vision for the
OL,13,Ffuture of Gloucestershire Airport.
OL,15,F"My team and I are excited to work
OL,16,Falongside Horizon during the due
OL,17,Fdiligence phase to assist the airport
OL,18,Fin transitioning to new ownership."
