OL,6,FThe business park expansion are part
OL,7,Fof plans to modernise the
OL,8,Finfrastructure, focusing on safety,
OL,9,Fefficiency, and digital innovation in
OL,10,Fline with the UK's Net Zero targets.
OL,12,FThe airport sits on a 375-acre site
OL,13,Fand Horizon now has planning consent
OL,14,Ffor an additional 30,000 square metres
OL,15,Fof business space.
OL,17,FThe council-owned airport in Staverton
OL,18,Fis said to have achieved more than its
OL,19,F#25million asking price but the exact
OL,20,Famount is not being revealed.
